<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<title>Image Seach Abstraction</title>

	<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.6/css/bootstrap.min.css">
</head>
<body>
	<h1 class="text-center">Image Search Abstraction Layer API</h1>
	<h3 class="text-center"> FreeCodeCamp Back-End API Section </h3>
	
	<div class="container">
		<h4>User Stories:  </h4>
		<ul>
			<li>I can get the image URLs, alt text and page urls for a set of images relating to a given search string.</li>
			<li> I can paginate through the responses by adding a ?offset=2 parameter to the URL.</li>
			<li>I can get a list of the most recently submitted search strings.</li>
		</ul>
	</div>

	<div class="container">
		<h3>Example calls to Bing Search: </h3>
		<br>
		<code>https://bungit.herokuapp.com/Drew Brees?offset=10</code><span>Results in image search results of the best NFL quarterback ever</span>
		<br>
		<code>https://bungit.herokuapp.com/prev</code><span>Results in recent searches</span>
	</div>

</body>
</html>